name: Escape From Tarkov "Killa's Helmet" and CHK-logo
description:
Escape From Tarkov is a realistic extraction MMORPG shooter created by BattleState Games based in Russia. The helmet depicted is of a boss within the game named "Killa"

The CHK stands for cheeki_scav a german EFT-Streamer, in cooperation with the Moondye7 Community
